wiki.summary: "BATTER UP" is the debut single by South Korean girl group BabyMonster. It was released on November 27, 2023, by YG Entertainment. The track was written by Jared Lee, Yang Hyun-suk, Asa of BabyMonster, Choi Hyun-suk of Treasure, Lee Chan-hyuk of AKMU, and songwriting teams Where the Noise and BigTone, and composed by Chaz Mishan, Yang Hyun-suk, Dee.P, Jared Lee, and Asa. It is described as a song with "hip-hop and trap" sounds characteristic of YG Entertainment. Read more on Last.fm.
